verbose_text: The transcriptional factor peroxisome proliferator activated receptor gamma coactivator-1 (PGC-1) stimulates GLUT4 expression in addition to stimulating mitochondrial biogenesis and promoting muscle remodeling to a fiber type composition that has greater oxidative capacity and less glycolytic metabolism in nature [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
evidence: GLUT4 expression in addition to stimulating mitochondrial biogenesis
